                      "fill": "$color-rich-soil",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "We help cooperatives and aligned organizations navigate the full lifecycle of their technology needs — from troubleshooting existing platforms and evaluating current systems, to integrating workflows across multiple platforms, recommending tailored solutions, vetting software vendors, onboarding staff onto new systems, and guiding transitions to open-source or values-aligned alternatives.",
