                      "fill": "$color-warm-white",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "When the right tool doesn't exist yet, we work alongside our partners to collaboratively design and build custom software from the ground up. Our deeply relational process ensures what we build is anchored in actual needs — from governance tools for cooperative decision-making, to member-facing platforms and tailored workflow applications.",
